OL,3,C'Seriously?': Government blasted over
OL,4,Cmedical scandal
OL,6,FProfessor Henrietta Hughes, Patient
OL,7,FSafety Commissioner, speaks to ITV
OL,8,FGranada's Political Correspondent Lise
OL,9,FMcNally to mark the two year
OL,10,Fanniversary of the Hughes Report.
OL,12,FIt is "disgraceful" the Government has
OL,13,Ffailed to respond to recommendations
OL,14,Fmade more than two years ago to
OL,15,Fcompensate victims of a medical
OL,16,Fscandal that left thousands of babies
OL,17,Fdisabled, England's first Patient
OL,18,FSafety Commissioner has said.
