OL,3,C'Seriously?': Government blasted over
OL,4,Cmedical scandal
OL,6,FThe Hughes Report - published on 7
OL,7,FFebruary 2024 - examined the impact
OL,8,Fthe epilepsy medication Sodium
OL,9,FValproate had on pregnant women and
OL,10,Ftheir unborn children.
OL,12,FIt recommended a compensation scheme
OL,13,Fbe set up, as well as quicker interim
OL,14,Fpayments to help families left in
OL,15,Ffinancial crisis.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
