OL,3,C'Seriously?': Government blasted over
OL,4,Cmedical scandal
OL,6,FBut so far, no payments have been
OL,7,Fmade. The Government has said it is
OL,8,F"carefully considering" the
OL,9,Frecommendations - but the Patient
OL,10,FSafety Commissioner says ministers
OL,11,Fmust not drag their feet.
OL,13,F"My message to the Government a year
OL,14,Fago was 'Just get on with it',"
OL,15,FProfessor Hughes told ITV News. "So
OL,16,Fwhat do I say two years down the line
OL,17,F- 'Seriously?'
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
