OL,3,C'Seriously?': Government blasted over
OL,4,Cmedical scandal
OL,6,F"We've been waiting for (the
OL,7,FGovernment's) response to
OL,8,Frecommendations that I was asked to
OL,9,Fmake by the Government. Two years on,
OL,10,FI haven't received a substantive
OL,11,Fresponse to my report.
OL,13,F"So as Patient Safety Commissioner,
OL,14,FI'm asking for a rapid response, rapid
OL,15,Faction, and for those patients and
OL,16,Ffamilies who've been harmed to be
OL,17,Ftreated with the dignity and respect
OL,18,Fthat they deserve.
OL,26,@nD@YpmoD@Mpn
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
