OL,3,C'Seriously?': Government blasted over
OL,4,Cmedical scandal
OL,6,F"It's frustrating for me, but all I
OL,7,Fcan say is, if I'm frustrated, I can
OL,8,Fonly imagine the level of frustration
OL,9,Ffor families who are affected."
OL,11,FSodium Valproate is an effective
OL,12,Ftreatment for epilepsy, but it can
OL,13,Fcause birth defects and developmental
OL,14,Fdelays to unborn children when
OL,15,Fprescribed to pregnant women - and
OL,16,Fover the last forty years thousands of
OL,17,Fmothers were given the drug by their
OL,18,Fdoctors, without being adequately
OL,19,Fwarned of the risks.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
