OL,3,C'Seriously?': Government blasted over
OL,4,Cmedical scandal
OL,6,FThe Patient Safety Commissioner
OL,7,Frecommended a compensation scheme
OL,8,Fsimilar to that given to victrims of
OL,9,Fthe infected blood scandal -
OL,10,Fpublishing a detailed report setting
OL,11,Fout how the scheme could work.
OL,13,F"When I published the report in 2024,
OL,14,FI said that these interim payments
OL,15,Fshould be started in 2025.
OL,17,F"It would allow patients and families
OL,18,Fto get some financial relief, but also
OL,19,Fallow us to understand the actual
OL,20,Fpopulation of people that have been
OL,21,Fharmed.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
