OL,3,C'Seriously?': Government blasted over
OL,4,Cmedical scandal
OL,6,F"We're now in 2026. So the
OL,7,Frecommendation that I made has already
OL,8,Fbeen bypassed."
OL,10,FProfessor Henrietta Hughes told ITV
OL,11,FNews she only agreed to carry out the
OL,12,Fwork in 2024, on the understanding
OL,13,Fthat it would lead to genuine action,
OL,14,Fand she says the lack of a response so
OL,15,Ffar has been devastating.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
