OL,3,C'Seriously?': Government blasted over
OL,4,Cmedical scandal
OL,6,F"I made it really clear that we should
OL,7,Fnot be asking patients and families to
OL,8,Fgo through very painful, personal and
OL,9,Fsensitive information with us if no
OL,10,Faction was going to be taken as a
OL,11,Fresult. It was on that basis that I
OL,12,Fagreed to do the work."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
