OL,3,C'Seriously?': Government blasted over
OL,4,Cmedical scandal
OL,6,F"Having been asked to do this piece of
OL,7,Fwork, not about whether patients
OL,8,Fshould receive financial redress, but
OL,9,Fhow they should receive financial
OL,10,Fredress, and then not to receive a
OL,11,Fresponse from the Government feels
OL,12,Fvery devastating to those families who
OL,13,Fshared that really sensitive personal
OL,14,Finformation with me."
OL,16,FThe Patient Safety Commissioner has
OL,17,Fnow used new powers granted to her
OL,18,Funder the Medicines and Medical
OL,19,FDevices Act, to press the Government
OL,20,Ffor details on what work had been done
OL,21,Fso far.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
