OL,3,C'Seriously?': Government blasted over
OL,4,Cmedical scandal
OL,6,FShe found details of when ministers,
OL,7,Fthe Health Secretary, Number 10, and
OL,8,Fthe Treasury were all briefed on the
OL,9,Fissue.
OL,11,F"So I now have that detail, but what I
OL,12,Fdon't have is that vital piece of
OL,13,Finformation, which is: What is missing
OL,14,Ffor the Government to be able to make
OL,15,Fa decision and respond to my
OL,16,Frecommendations?"
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
