OL,3,C'Seriously?': Government blasted over
OL,4,Cmedical scandal
OL,6,FProfessor Hughes says she will now be
OL,7,Fdirectly approaching Number 10 Downing
OL,8,FStreet, to secure financial redress
OL,9,Ffor victims of Sodium Valproate, as
OL,10,Fwell as those harmed by pelvic mesh
OL,11,Fimplants.
OL,13,F"This is unfinished business. This is
OL,14,Fa disgraceful way that patients and
OL,15,Ffamilies are being treated by those in
OL,16,Fpower. And what I would say is - if
OL,17,Fit's not safe care, it's not care at
OL,18,Fall."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
