OL,3,C'Seriously?': Government blasted over
OL,4,Cmedical scandal
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the Department of
OL,7,FHealth and Social Care told ITV News
OL,8,F"We recognise the significant impact
OL,9,Fthat sodium valproate and pelvic mesh
OL,10,Fhave had on people and their families.
OL,12,F"This is a complex issue and our
OL,13,Fpriority is to ensure any response is
OL,14,Ffair, balanced and sensitive to those
OL,15,Faffected. We are carefully considering
OL,16,Fthe recommendations within the Hughes
OL,17,FReport, in collaboration with relevant
OL,18,Fdepartments, and we aim to provide an
OL,19,Fupdate in due course"
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/13
